Package com.sailthru.mobile.sdk.interfaces

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ContentIntentBuilder
    Implement this interface to build a custom intent to be executed when the notification is tapped Note: Direct to URI notifications using the _u parameter will never call {@link #build(Context, Bundle)}
    Logger
    Logging interface to capture logging coming from the Sailthru Mobile SDK.
    NotificationActionTappedListener
    Listener used to identify when a notification action was tapped
    NotificationReceivedListener
    Listener used to identify when a notification was received
    NotificationSilencer
    Implement NotificationSilencer if you want to suppress any received notification to be presented by Sailthru Mobile
    NotificationTappedListener
    Listener used to identify when a notification was tapped
